<div class="flush-right col-md-6 macrium-reflect-text">
<h1>What is Macrium Reflect?</h1>
<p>Macrium Reflect is image based backup and cloning software.</p>
<p>Macrium Reflect creates an accurate and reliable image of a hard disk or the partitions on the disk. In the event of a partial or complete system loss, you can use this image to restore the entire disk, one or more partitions, or even individual files and folders.</p>
<p>Using Macrium Reflect you can backup whole partitions or individual files and folders into a single compressed, mountable archive file. You can use this archive to restore exact images of the partitions on a hard disk so that you can easily upgrade your hard disk or recover your system if it breaks. You can also mount images as a virtual drive in Windows Explorer to easily recover Files and Folders using Copy and Paste.</p>
</div>
